file name-data.txt  output: Hello Python

Read Entire File:

file = open("data.txt", "r")
content = file.read()
print(content)
file.close()

Read Line by Line:

file = open("data.txt", "r")
for line in file:
    print(line)
file.close()

Best Practice (with)-automatically closes the file

with open("data.txt", "r") as file:
    content = file.read()
print(content)
